This project is an adaptation of the work by Malafeev et al. (2021):

Malafeev A, Hertig-Godeschalk A, Schreier DR, Skorucak J, Mathis J, Achermann P (2021)
Automatic Detection of Microsleep Episodes with Deep Learning.
Front. Neurosci. 15:564098. doi: 10.3389/fnins.2021.564098

Dataset: Dryad Drowsiness Dataset
https://datadryad.org/dataset/doi:10.5061/dryad.5tb2rbp9c

